---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Currency
description: "Browse Openflows Currency entries across Currents, Circuits, and Practitioners in the open source AI ecosystem."
permalink: /currency/
---

<section class="hero-panel">
  <div>
    <p class="hero-kicker">Knowledge navigation</p>
    <h2>Currency is the living layer of Openflows.</h2>
    <p>Currency tracks what is moving as conditions change. Currents hold provisional signals, Circuits name stabilized patterns, and Practitioners mark sustained methods of shaping the field.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-grid">
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.currents.length }}</strong><span>Currents</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.circuits.length }}</strong><span>Circuits</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.practitioners.length }}</strong><span>Practitioners</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><strong>{{ collections.zh_currency.length }}</strong><span>Chinese entries</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

{% set browserId = "currency-browser-en" %}
{% include "currency-browser.njk" %}

<section class="section-band">
  <div class="grid-list">
    <article class="hub-card">
      <h3><a href="/currency/currents/">Currents</a></h3>
      <p class="meta">{{ collections.currents.length }} entries</p>
      <p>Provisional movement: signals, tensions, and early patterning from the open source AI ecosystem.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="hub-card">
      <h3><a href="/currency/circuits/">Circuits</a></h3>
      <p class="meta">{{ collections.circuits.length }} entries</p>
      <p>Completed loops: synthesized patterns that have stabilized across multiple currents.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="hub-card">
      <h3><a href="/currency/practitioners/">Practitioners</a></h3>
      <p class="meta">{{ collections.practitioners.length }} entries</p>
      <p>Those who have shaped the field through sustained practice and inspectable work.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="currency-section">
  <div class="currency-section-header">
    <h2>Recent Currents</h2>
    <span class="entry-count muted">{{ collections.currents.length }} entries</span>
  </div>
  <ul class="currency-list">
    {% for item in collections.currents %}
      {% if loop.index0 < 5 %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
        {% if item.data.abstract %}<p class="item-abstract">{{ item.data.abstract }}</p>{% endif %}
        <div class="item-meta">
          <span class="muted">{{ item.date | readableDate }}</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
